9-01T00:42:12.000Z","msg":"CJ<br />\nCJ<br />\n1 年前 (已編輯)<br />\n馬斯克為什麼做特斯拉？因為以內燃機為主的交通工具和動力無法在火星工作。<br />\n馬斯克為什麼收購 Solar City？因為各種資源缺發的火星上，以太陽能發電的最合適。<br />\n馬斯克為什麼創造Space X？因為馬斯克目標將百萬人送往火星，不管是便宜可回收的火箭，或是能用於降落時的反推動技術，都是必須的。<br />\n馬斯克為什麼需要The Boring Company？火星上沒氧氣，在真空下Hyperloop的技術，將有更有效率的交通，更可將交通由二維空間架為三維。<br />\n馬斯克為什麼著手Starlink？火星上，人到了、能源解決了、交通、吃喝穩定後，需要的是通訊技術（Wifi）。利用1.2萬顆衛星作連結，不管之後是向地球或火星內部的通訊，都需要行星的級別技術。<br />\n馬斯克為什麼創業Neuralink？未來社會人類交互，人機結合傳遞訊息才有望突破利用語言線性輸出、解碼的效率低下。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube有人咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59dbaac5c717fe75d75d01fa1eb637a5ef6caf41","tid":2183282,"uid":20368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:42:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa940e3403a3c30755bbad140a89b28c390746fd","tid":2183282,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:44:44.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7sTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=3323ba07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"},{"pid":"246f0d9b2c6c6cb45a3337d82196d9997d244de5","tid":2183282,"uid":103929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a59cbfe48ad6108f6c12a9ac2830781c6ff3c04","tid":2183282,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2b323ed9cf25913b13ee0ebb6d6c79d9690dfc1","tid":2183282,"uid":103929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:33:41.000Z","msg":"話做肯定無難度<br />\n科技本身3年就一個層次<br />\n50年內高達無難度"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T00:39:34.000Z","msg":"整黎冇用，又坐唔到幾多條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /